<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.5.2">
<l>taṇkaṭal vaṭṭat tuḷḷārait tamakkirai yāttaṭin tuṇṇun</l>
<l>tiṇkaḻaṟ kālacu rarkkut tīṅkiḻaik kuntiru mālai</l>
<l>paṇka ṭalaikkoḷḷap pāṭip paṟantuṅ kuṉittu muḻalātār</l>
<l>maṇko ḷulakiṟ piṟappār valviṉai mōta malaintē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Tirumāl who does harm to the Asuras with firm anklets on [their] feet</l>
<l>who cut [and] eat as their food those who are in the circle [surrounded] by the cool sea,</l>
<l>those who don’t roam, spreading and bowing in song on him, as the melodies take hold [of them],</l>
<l>they will be [re]born in the earth world, begin opposed as [their] harsh karma strikes.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
